              <p style="font-size: var(--h1-font-size);">At üçÄSENIORITY, we utilise cutting-edge Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning (ML) techniques to encourage cognitive decline prevention.</p>
              <p style="font-size: var(--h1-font-size);">1. Choose one category between history/sports/music. Random Wikipedia articles from that category will be assigned to you.</p>
